            "answer_text": "If the sum of 2 angles is less than 360\u00b0, then they can be adjacent. Since an obtuse angle is less than 180\u00b0, the sum of 2 obtuse angles will always be less than 360\u00b0. Hence, 2 obtuse angles can be adjacent angles. ",
